Talent level 10 Upgrade Abyssal Hand
increase base damage by 3
increase scaling by 7%
increase total mana cost reduce by 10%
increase health Threshold by 10%
increase mana cost by 90

add a new modifier Hand of Despair
Enemys will have 50% chance to feel Despair in their souls dealing 10 plus 25% of Esharad inteillgence every 0.5 seconds for 3.0 seconds
and every tick of damage will have 12% chance to reduce the target armor by 3, magic resist by 6% and increasing pure damage taken by 3%
that last 6.5 seconds. increase the duration of Hand of Dispair by 0.1 seconds for every 4 inteillgence. Esharad will gain a stack of
Despair if the target dies under Hand of Despair, each stacks will give 12 mana and 1 inteillgence max of 20. At 8 stacks, Hand of
Despair will gain 0.5 duration and every 0.2 seconds the target will suffer -0.07 health regeneration that last 1.6 seconds and refresh
every tick of Health regeneration lost. at 15 stacks, Abbysal Hand will gain 0.80 root duration and increase the health threshold by 15%
and also reduce its coldown by 5. 7 stacks are lost on death and 1 stack is lost upon getting silence.


SPELL W Fearing Gaze
Esharad Gaze upon his target enemy or allys. Enemys will take medium amount of damage and their base magic resist will be reduce to a
value, they cannot increase it but can be lower. Enemys will also suffer from health and mana regeneration lost for a short time and
Esharad will gain that health and mana regeneration they lose. Gazing into a ally will give them increase attack damage and spellamp for
4.5 seconds and reducing Fearing Gaze coldown by 40%. Fearing Gaze will also have 16% chance to fear the target for 1.3 seconds and
dealing 5 10 15 20 25 30 35 extra base damage as well. this spell will gain 2.1% increase damage and 4.3% manacost increase for every
level of Esharad. Also increase Mana and Mana regeneration. Esharad cannot self cast Fearing Gaze and allys can also be fear but will
not take the extra damage.

base damage 14 plus 18% of inteillgence
Health regeneration lost -6.0 plus 10% of Inteillgence
Mana regeneration lost -3.0 plus 15% of inteillgence
Base magic resist reduce -13%
debuff duration 4.5 seconds
Attack damage increase 22%
Spellamp increase 11%
Bonus Mana 4% 7% 11% 15% 19% 24% 30%
Bonus Mana regeneration 1.3 1.9 2.4 3.3 4.5 5.9 7.5
